Gigs.MoreInfo:
Why not start your weekend early and come and see 80's legend CHESNEY HAWKES live on stage at REFLEX BLACKPOOL!!

It's all happening on Thursday 30th June - an amazing night with cheap drinks plus "THE ONE & ONLY" CHESNEY HAWKES!!!

Open all day, party starts at 8pm, Chesney live from 10pm!!!

Reflex Blackpool is located at the Foxhall - almost opposite Central Pier. It's going to be an amazing night!

Hope you can join us
Gigs.GigTitle: Chesney Hawkes - Live at REFLEX BLACKPOOL!!!
